Subject: Re: Evaluation Board details.

Hi Sri and Biju,
I would like to share an update on the initial bring-up of the ATSAME70Q21 =
evaluation kit.
The development environment was successfully set up using MPLAB X IDE and t=
he XC32 compiler, along with the required SAME70 Device Family Pack. Develo=
pment was carried out using the MPLAB Harmony 3 CSP framework.
As part of the validation, a basic GPIO LED control application was impleme=
nted and tested. The application performs LED ON/OFF and LED blinking opera=
tions, confirming successful programming of the device and correct operatio=
n of the MCU, clock, GPIO, and debug interface.
The evaluation kit is confirmed to be functional and ready for further deve=
lopment. I have handed over the device along with the USB Type-A cable to A=
bhinaya. Biju and the team will have a discussion next week regarding the s=
teps to be followed. Once the meeting is completed, Will update you on the =
next course of action.
Regards,
Midhun Abraham.

