Hi Sir,

I have looked into it, and the Microchip ATSAM family does support GCC-base=
d toolchains. Specifically, it is compatible with ARM GCC and can be used w=
ith Microchip=92s MPLAB X IDE along with Atmel Studio.

Regards,
Midhun Abraham
