Subject: Evaluation Board details.

Dear Biju,
I have reviewed some available evaluation boards and compiled a list for yo=
ur reference, which is attached to this email.
Among the options, the NXP S32K144 EVB-Q100 appears to be the most suitable=
 and preferred choice based on documentations and resources.
Could you kindly review the details and help me in finalizing the selection=
 of the evaluation board?
Best regards,
Midhun Abraham.



